---
import Influences from "../components/Influences.astro";
import MyStack from "../components/MyStack.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "../consts";
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base keywords="" title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
  <main class="main-content">
    <div class="about-content-wrapper comeFromBelow f-jc-center f-wrap">
      <article class="about-content">
        <img src="/placeholder-about.jpg" />
        <h1>👻 Greetings to the fellow geeks</h1>
        <p>
          Hi, I'm Darián López, A mathematician turned software developer 😎.
        </p>
        <p>
          Currently working on continuous learning and having no "zero days".
          Most of my professional experience comes from software development and
          technical lead in the most diverse sectors, focused on web
          development.
        </p>
        <p>
          Fancied of music, simplicity and beaty of applied maths, and
          videogames. I find that high level languages/tools and the low level
          counterpart complements each other, and the journey to mastering
          something involves getting things done and "reinvent the wheel" in
          equal parts.
        </p>

        <p>
          Here are a few topics that interests me and probably will be writing
          about:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>🕸️ Web development, mostly react 👽. Yeah, i know, i know ...</li>
          <li>🕹️ Videogames, of course.</li>
          <li>⚙️ Graphics programming. (Game engine I really hope 🤞)</li>
          <li>🐢 Software engineering.</li>
          <li>🦥 Automation for really lazy people like me</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
    <MyStack />
    <Influences />
  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-content-wrapper {
    gap: 20px;
  }
  img {
    /* margin-bottom: auto; */
    margin-top: 20px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    width: 100%;
    height: 250px;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    /* margin: var(--v-gap-l) var(--h-gap-l); */
  }
  .about-content {
    /* max-width: 600px; */
    width: 100%;
  }
  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    img {
      height: 500px;
      float: right;
      width: min(350px, 90%);
      margin: var(--v-gap) var(--h-gap);
    }
  }
</style>
